{"tid":654155,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人買過Kindle，好唔好用","createTime":"2018-05-05T11:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T15:32:00.000Z","uid":129134,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e44149a849ab73906ef13f9bb1196b5e850d8668","tid":654155,"uid":129134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:24:19.000Z","msg":"我個背囊因袋書所以好重，唔知好唔好買kindle用<br />\nKindle支唔支援中文？會唔會好快無電？多唔多書買？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4cc635daabbb6aa75af1f0408e07877cbed418f","tid":654155,"uid":121409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:30:28.000Z","msg":"電好持久，支援中文，但amazon冇繁體書賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我平時會喺kobo買完轉入kindle，你未買可以考慮直接買kobo嗰部，或者台灣出嗰部mooink，可以直接買繁體書<br />\n好唔好用好睇你睇開咩書，睇小說嗰啲唔錯，夠輕同埋幾時睇都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但textbook或者工具書科普書，要成日跳頁睇我就覺得麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8378d44a05299ac95c010434827e7ab22a625d44","tid":654155,"uid":114434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:34:47.000Z","msg":"好好用<br />\n電量多，中文冇問題，又撞得跌得。<br />\n最緊要買有背燈款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb761069707ab6234342dbf9b179bc49e46def1","tid":654155,"uid":185162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:50:17.000Z","msg":"好好用，輕身，唔帶袋出街都得，隨時一百幾十本書可以揀來睇。可以去好讀網下載繁體字書，數量其實唔算非常多，但一般閱讀來說已經非常足夠。舊版唔貴，抵買。"},{"pid":"146f70a929aa0b61e673b11e5258938a73f5d98c","tid":654155,"uid":17875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8378d44a05299ac95c010434827e7ab22a625d44","tid":654155,"uid":114434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:34:47.000Z","msg":"好好用<br />\n電量多，中文冇問題，又撞得跌得。<br />\n最緊要買有背燈款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy